  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 21:15-16",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1 Chronicles 21:15-16",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "God sent an angel unto Jerusalem to destroy it, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — This seems to import that there were more angels than one employed to effect this destruction in different parts of the country: and that the angels, sent to Jerusalem, had begun to slay some of its inhabitants. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The Lord beheld, and repented him of the evil — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Probably because he beheld their serious repentance. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "David and the elders clothed in sackcloth — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, in mourning garments; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "fell on their faces — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Humbling themselves before God for their sins, and deprecating his wrath against the people. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
